es:**\n- **Timeline Room:** Navigate through a beautifully designed VR space where all your timelines are displayed. \n- **View Moments:** Relive your photos, and writings in an immersive environment. Each timeline is a gallery of your life's unique moments.\n- **VR Museum:** See your life\u2019s story unfold in a virtual reality museum. Every moment is a piece of art, brought to life in VR.\n\nBecause every moment of life is unique, Lifestory lets you etch them forever on secure timelines and experience them in a whole new way.", "short_description": "Step into the Timeline Room and immerse yourself in your life's moments with Lifestory on Meta Quest. Navigate through a virtual reality museum where your timelines and memories come to life."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://api.lifestoryapp.com/static/html/terms.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Lifestory", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://lifestoryapp.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1819021644882647"}, {"id": "1228796255027646"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7669651099782639"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "423053657368824"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "423053657368824"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1720428787, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "423053657368824"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes